  "text": "induction. As shown in Fig. 1C , a drop in survival rates ranging from 8-10 hours to 16 hours was found in all three CLP groups, and it was during this period that the maximum host immune responses, including bacterial dissemination and inflammation, occurred [CITATION_1] . At 48 hours, mice in the BzATP-treated group, control group, and the A740003-treated group exhibited mortalities of 91%, 86%, and 73%, respectively. No significant differences were observed between the BzATP-treated/A740003-treated mice and the CLP mice (p > 0.05).",
